Case Study 1: The Gambler
body:
With an assisting officer, you then undertake a frisk. Here is what you discover: 

  • Bulges on the female’s waist – bundles of something taped to her waist 
  • Bulges on the male’s lower legs – bundles of something taped to his legs.
